Product.Description: Loyalty plans offer special fixed rates exclusively for loyal Spark Energy customers. Thank you for allowing us to serve you.

Want to reduce your carbon footprint? Through the purchase of carbon offsets, our carbon neutral plan offsets the carbon emissions created by the natural gas you consume. Plus, your commodity rate stays put, guaranteed, for 12 months. With this rate, there’s a $100 early cancellation fee and a $4.95 monthly service fee.
